    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, showcasing impeccable mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight with zero lash. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Every seal is supple, and the undercarriage is devoid of oxidation. A true turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
